会话中未被提及或解决，故保留。\",\"inContractCode\":\"TG2312551486\",\"aiRobotUserId\":\"31653746\",\"triggerSource\":10,\"workflowRunId\":\"RUN-2606291606200081876756\",\"robotWeworkId\":\"31151561\",\"aiRobotUcId\":1000000031653746,\"sessionId\":\"new_session_id:SERVICE_KEEPER--GROUP_CHAT--10754215018509011--2#1782706701000\",\"datacenterHost\":\"http://app-center-huiju-cloudkeeper-datacenter.ke.com\",\"userName\":\"上海贝壳租房服务管家惠荏\",\"userId\":1000000022170187,\"aiType\":2,\"ruleHost\":\"http://rule.cloudkeeper.huiju.ke.com\",\"msgTime\":\"2026-06-29 16:06:00\",\"senderType\":1,\"inContractId\":1083378,\"resblockId\":\"5011000010691\",\"contractCode\":\"TGCF2605903902\"},\"requestId\":\"1192841\",\"result\":true,\"sessionId\":\"SYS0aadf6b8-1648-4c3e-bc32-3f9521a090e7\"}",
