inContractCode\":\"TG2312551486\",\"aiRobotUserId\":\"31653746\",\"triggerSource\":10,\"workflowRunId\":\"RUN-2606291606220090879165\",\"robotWeworkId\":\"31151561\",\"aiRobotUcId\":1000000031653746,\"sessionId\":\"new_session_id:SERVICE_KEEPER--GROUP_CHAT--10754215018509011--2#1782706701000\",\"datacenterHost\":\"http://app-center-huiju-cloudkeeper-datacenter.ke.com\",\"userName\":\"上海贝壳租房服务管家惠荏\",\"userId\":1000000022170187,\"imgConvertText\":\"【图片类型】\n手机截图\n\n【图片内容】\n页面标题为“设置密码”，显示手机号码为+86 15****10，右侧有“获取验证码”按钮。下方有两个输入框，分别为“请输入验证码”和“请输入新密码（最少8位，数字+字母）”。底部有一个蓝色的“提交”按钮。页面顶部显示时间为16:01，信号为5G，电池电量充足。\n\n【图片目的】\n展示当前截图内容\n\n【是否屋内设施照片】\n否\n\n【匹配商品】\n无\n\n【是否对账图片】\n否\",\"aiType\":2,\"ruleHost\":\"http://rule.cloudkeeper.huiju.ke.com\",\"msgTime\":\"2026-06-29 16:01:45\",\"senderType\":4,\"inContractId\":1083378,\"resblockId\":\"5011000010691\",\"contractCode\":\"TGCF2605903902\"},\"requestId\":\"2572866\",\"result\":true,\"sessionId\":\"SYS902095e6-f9f6-4b26-ac5e-cc68265fd258\"}",
